title: 2BR 2BA Apartment homes with great lighting!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
